#Installation

```` 
$ wget http://redis.googlecode.com/files/redis-2.4.15.tar.gz
$ tar xzf redis-2.4.15.tar.gz
$ cd redis-2.4.15
$ make
````

##Simple Test

*run server*

```` 
$src/redis-server
````

*run client*

```` 
$ src/redis-cli
redis> set foo bar
OK
redis> get foo
"bar"
````

这里是一个[在线教程](http://try.redis-db.com/)
